entries:
  QL_MinakkareMini_Dragonfly_Desc:
    contents:
      - text: "Jana wants to give her insect-loving little\nsister, Gleema, a birthday gift. But no matter\nhow many times Jana asks, Gleema won't tell\nher what kind of bug she wants.\n\nYou should talk to "
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: red
      - text: Gleema
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: " for the full story."
  QL_MinakkareMini_Dragonfly_Dragonfly:
    contents:
      - text: "Despite Jana's severe aversion to dragonflies,\nshe's determined to give her little sister\nthe birthday gift she wants.\n\nBring "
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: red
      - text: Jana
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: " one "
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: red
      - text: warm darner
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: ", one "
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: red
      - text: cold darner
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: ",\nand one "
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: red
      - text: electric darner
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "."
  QL_MinakkareMini_Dragonfly_Finish:
    contents:
      - text: "You gave Gleema the warm darner,\ncold darner, and electric darner.\n\nJana gave you a reward for all your trouble."
  QL_MinakkareMini_Dragonfly_Give:
    contents:
      - text: "You gave Gleema the warm darner,\ncold darner, and electric darner.\n\nIn her excitement, she forgot herself and\nrushed to show Jana. Can "
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: red
      - text: Jana
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "'s nerves\ntake the strain?"
  QL_MinakkareMini_Dragonfly_LittleSister:
    contents:
      - text: "Gleema told you that she loves dragonflies\nabove all other insects, but Jana can't stand\nthe sight of them. You now understand why\nGleema can't tell her sister what she wants.\n\nYou'll have to tell "
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: red
      - text: Jana
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: " so the two of you can\ndecide what to do."
  QL_MinakkareMini_Dragonfly_Name:
    contents:
      - text: "Little Sister's Big Request"
  QL_MinakkareMini_Dragonfly_Through:
    contents:
      - text: "Unsurprisingly, Jana couldn't bring herself to\ntake the dragonflies from you.\n\nGive "
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: red
      - text: Gleema
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: " the "
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: red
      - text: warm darner
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: ", "
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: red
      - text: cold darner
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: ",\nand "
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: red
      - text: electric darner
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: " yourself."
